Source: thailatex
Section: tex
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Theppitak Karoonboonyanan <thep@linux.thai.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>=4.0.0)
Build-Depends-Indep: texlive-font-utils, texlive-latex-base, tex-common (>=0.19), gs-common
Standards-Version: 3.7.2.2

Package: thailatex
Architecture: all 
Recommends: swath|cttex
Depends: texlive-base-bin, texlive-latex-base, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Thai Latex package
 This package provides Thai language add-on for Latex. It is based on 
 babel package which comes with tetex distribution.
 .
 This package needs Thai words separator such as cttex and swath, in
 order for latex to be able to break sentences.
